com.cisco.pxgrid.util

Class GenericMessageContentExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cisco.pxgrid.util.GenericMessageContentExtractor

  • public abstract class GenericMessageContentExtractor
extends Object
    A content extractor to properly retrieve the content based on the content type

    Sample usage:

    GenericMessageContent content;

    GenericMessageContentExtractor extractor = GenericMessageContentExtractor.newExtractor(content);

    byte[] rawContent = extractor.extractRaw();

    String plainTextContent = extractor.extractPlainText();

    Object pxGridModelContent = extractor.extractPxGridModel();

    Author:
    anto
